<button type="button" class="pull-right btn btn-danger btn-lg navigation" ng-click="exit()">
  Cancel
</button>  
<h3 class="wizard-title">
  Calibrate Extruder Offset
</h3>
<div class="clearfix"><br/></div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <p>To precisely calibrate the offset between the two extruder nozzles, the current offset is
      set to factory defaults and a calibration print created to measure the mechanical deviation:</p>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" ng-click="generate_printjob()">
      Reset Offset & Add Calibration Printjob to Queue
    </button>
    <br/>
    <br/>    
    <p>After printing visually select the line number for X and Y where both single line
      extrusions (bottom layer and top layer) vertically align with each other.</p>
     <h4 class="text-center">
      X:
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg keypad" ng-click="dec_x()">-</button>                    
      &nbsp;<b>{{ line_x }}</b>&nbsp;
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg keypad" ng-click="inc_x()">+</button>
    </h4>
     <h4 class="text-center">
      Y:
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg keypad" ng-click="dec_y()">-</button>                    
      &nbsp;<b>{{ line_y }}</b>&nbsp;
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg keypad" ng-click="inc_y()">+</button>
    </h4>    
    <button type="button" class="pull-right btn btn-primary btn-lg navigation" ng-click="save()">
      Save Calibration
    </button>     
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <!-- picture: calibration pattern -->
    <img src="<%= asset_path("touchapp/images/wizard_calibrate_offset_pattern.jpg") %>" class="img-responsive">    
  </div> 
</div>
